title: Eddie Sees a Celebrity in the Wild + Lunchbox Pitches A Valentine’s Day Business Idea + Our Dream Guest List
itunes:title: Eddie Sees a Celebrity in the Wild + Lunchbox Pitches A Valentine’s Day Business Idea + Our Dream Guest List
description:
Eddie tells us about the A-List celebrity he saw out in public and was surprised no one was bothering them. Lunchbox tells us about a new business idea he has where he is squatting on Valentine’s Day reservations. He asks if anyone wants to get in on the business. We reveal what celebrities would be on our dream guest list and if we could get them.
